# Docker Guidelines

- Use Docker Compose to manage multi-container applications.
- If a service inside `docker-compose.yml` file becomes too large, break it into a corresponding `Dockerfile`.
- Use the new `docker compose` command (without a hyphen) instead of the deprecated `docker-compose`.
